+ Creating Storage\nCredentials
++ Azure steps
+++_ Create Access Connector (same region as storage)
+++_ Choose system- or user-assigned MI
+++_ Grant Storage Blob Data Contributor\non ADLS account/container
+++_ (Optional) Storage Queue Data Contributor
++++_ Enables file event notifications
++ Unity Catalog steps
+++_ Catalog Explorer → Credentials
+++_ Select Azure Managed Identity
+++_ Provide Access Connector resource ID
+++_ Provide user-assigned MI ID (if applicable)
++ Prerequisite
+++_ CREATE STORAGE CREDENTIAL on metastore
+++_ Account admin / metastore admin by default
@endmindmap
